																<div class="mh-custom-posts-content">
									<div class="mh-custom-posts-header">
										<h3 class="mh-custom-posts-xl-title">
											<a href="https://www.overclockers.com/colorful-igame-x870e-vulcan-oc-v14-motherboard-review/" title="Colorful iGame X870E VULCAN OC V14 Motherboard Review">
												Colorful iGame X870E VULCAN OC V14 Motherboard Review											</a>
										</h3>
										<div class="mh-meta entry-meta">
<span class="entry-meta-date updated"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i><a href="https://www.overclockers.com/2026/05/">May 14, 2026</a></span>
<span class="entry-meta-comments"><i class="fa fa-comment-o"></i><a href="https://www.overclockers.com/colorful-igame-x870e-vulcan-oc-v14-motherboard-review/#comments" class="mh-comment-count-link" >4</a></span>
</div>
									</div>
									<div class="mh-excerpt"><p>We rarely get to review Colorful&#8217;s products, but they&#8217;re always unique and interesting. This time, we received the latest overclocking-series motherboard for AMD Ryzen processors: the iGame X870E VULCAN OC V14. The motherboard is optimized for the latest AMD Ryzen 9000 processors from the X3D series and high-frequency DDR5 memory. It&#8217;s also packed with gaming and overclocking features, which we cover in our review. <a class="mh-excerpt-more" href="https://www.overclockers.com/colorful-igame-x870e-vulcan-oc-v14-motherboard-review/" title="Colorful iGame X870E VULCAN OC V14 Motherboard Review"></a></p>
</div>								</div>
							</div>
